%% Sequence 5 - Use case: Reject an invalid submission (exception flow)
%% Two failure paths: caught in the browser, and caught by the API contract.
sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    actor U as User
    participant UI as Browser page
    participant API as FastAPI route
    participant SC as ScanRequest schema
    participant AN as RiskAnalyzer

    U->>UI: click Scan with an empty field
    UI->>UI: validate input is not blank
    UI-->>U: "Enter a URL to scan."
    Note over UI,API: no request is sent - fails fast in the client

    U->>UI: submit a malformed request body
    UI->>API: POST /scan {}
    API->>SC: validate against ScanRequest
    SC-->>API: ValidationError - 'url' field required
    API-->>UI: 422 Unprocessable Entity
    Note over API,AN: RiskAnalyzer is never reached
    UI->>UI: catch non-OK response
    UI-->>U: "Could not reach the scanner."
